item.title: JDK thingy
item.dc:creator: @novalye Novalye
item.description:
@novalye wrote:

Once you downloaded JDK 3 re-edit your compiler to look like this
@echo off
title Server Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
pause

Hope this helped.=)
